<ul>
  <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Email address when you sign in using email/password or Google Sign-In.</li>
  <li><strong>User Content:</strong Photos, videos, and milestone data you create inside the app.</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. How We Store Your Data</h2>

<p>All photos, videos, and personal content are stored locally on your device using secure storage (SQLite database and device file system).</p>

<p>We do not upload or share your private media to external servers unless explicitly stated in future updates.</p>

<h2>3. Google Sign-In</h2>

