<p>Your data is used only to provide core app functionality, including:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Saving and displaying your milestones</li>
  <li>Managing your account</li>
</ul>

<h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>

<p>We do not sell, trade, or share your personal data with third parties.</p>

<h2>6. Data Security</h2>

<p>We take reasonable measures to protect your data. However, no method of storage is 100% secure.</p>

<h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>

<p>This app may contain content related to children (such as baby milestones), but it is intended for use by parents or guardians.</p>

<p>We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>

<h2>8. Your Rights</h2>

<p>You can:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Delete your data by removing the app from your device</li>
  <li>Stop using the service at any time</li>
